  "title": "Text Reference Section",
  "html": "<h1 id=\"text-reference-section\"><a href=\"#text-reference-section\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Text Reference Section</h1></p><p>Displays long-form text, paragraphs, articles, and reference content.</p><p><h2 id=\"overview\"><a href=\"#overview\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Overview</h2></p><p>The <strong>Text Reference Section</strong> (<code>type: \"text-reference\"</code>) is used for displays long-form text, paragraphs, articles, and reference content.</p><p><h3 id=\"quick-facts\"><a href=\"#quick-facts\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Quick Facts</h3></p><p><div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table><thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Value</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Type</td><td><code>text-reference</code></td></tr><tr><td>Uses Fields</td><td>Yes</td></tr><tr><td>Uses Items</td><td>No</td></tr><tr><td>Default Columns</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>Supports Collapse</td><td>Yes</td></tr><tr><td>Aliases</td><td><code>reference</code>, <code>text-ref</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div></p><p><h2 id=\"use-cases\"><a href=\"#use-cases\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Use Cases</h2></p><p><ul><li>Articles</li><li>Blog posts</li><li>Research summaries</li><li>Long-form content</li></ul>\n<h2 id=\"data-schema\"><a href=\"#data-schema\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Data Schema</h2></p><p><h3 id=\"fields-schema\"><a href=\"#fields-schema\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Fields Schema</h3></p><p><div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table><thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>label</code></td><td>string</td><td>Reference label</td></tr><tr><td><code>value</code></td><td>string</td><td>Reference title/name</td></tr><tr><td><code>text</code></td><td>string</td><td>Reference text content</td></tr><tr><td><code>description</code></td><td>string</td><td>Reference description</td></tr><tr><td><code>url</code></td>